{"tid":2440389,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"梁競徽拍抗日神劇","createTime":"2021-03-10T02:17:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T04:00:23.000Z","uid":228360,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"380ee37a836899842cf2fef946dfaa61267c9335","tid":2440389,"uid":228360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T02:17:19.000Z","msg":"原名梁烈唯嘅梁競徽近年積極喺內地發展，頻頻喺微博向中國示忠，近排終於有機會拍內地製作嘅抗日Cult片《浴血狂蟒》，仲好威水咁擔正做男一添呀！<br />\n內地觀眾鍾意嘅電影類型同香港觀眾唔同，如果電影有講怪獸及軍人元素，通常都有唔錯票房。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RgbGmGp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRgbGmGp.jpg&h=e9fbe98b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0BTESOn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0BTESOn.jpg&h=2db24346&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Gd9vz2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Gd9vz2.jpg&h=067b22fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次《浴血狂蟒》當然離不開呢個類型，故事講述1945年緬北滇西反攻戰中，中國軍人入緬支援英軍作戰，點知喺戰鬥中三架飛虎隊戰機被日軍擊落，軍人留落雲南原始森林大娘山中發現日方研究生化武器，搞到叢林裡嘅動物變得狂暴，其中一條巨蟒變得狂暴嗜殺，令全部人都好危險。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xKGStms.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxKGStms.jpg&h=033a079b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n戲中做男一嘅梁競徽留咗鬚及操fit咗身型，轉型行成熟路線，中佬味濃。佢早兩日喺微博上載多張劇照並留言話：「是日拍攝完成～回去梳洗～非常開心可以參與這次拍攝～中國軍人～就是牛！保家衛國！這是我們的使命。」。呢個PO一出，唔少內地網民紛紛留言支持及大讚佢好有型，例如「期待徽哥的新作品！」、「徽哥新角色，支持，期待上映」、「帥哦 辛苦了」、「太帥了，期待新作。」、「好有型，眼神殺死人，戰狼3預埋你」、「你好帥」及「好好好，多來内地拍戲，你值得」等等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n柒到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯唯不如改名叫勁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"242731804e5c1aed57551b52ab9f38038d9452a3","tid":2440389,"uid":90820,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T02:27:46.000Z","msg":"讀得書少<br />\n而家先知保安英文係Baoan<br />\n但點解要寫Chinese唔寫Zhongguoren呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/omhRJYC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FomhRJYC.jpg&h=38dfee7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7361a9783e982307dc7d6eae875c3b4cc53c1f9c","tid":2440389,"uid":284104,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T02:30:56.000Z","msg":"//中國軍人～就是牛！//<br />\n姐係話緊中國軍人唔係人係畜牲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed07c20973c35e9139fd9826a44e672d2c724e0","tid":2440389,"uid":359589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T02:31:34.000Z","msg":"造型好過鳩柏豪嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c041590a1e346bbb4bc785524ef278b1730fe23","tid":2440389,"uid":236891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T02:32:31.000Z","msg":"條垃圾終於有嘢撈"},{"pid":"7ccd4ddc40b6e85ba8ba43354527e809ffc204c0","tid":2440389,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7361a9783e982307dc7d6eae875c3b4cc53c1f9c","tid":2440389,"uid":284104,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T02:30:56.000Z","msg":"//中國軍人～就是牛！//<br />\n姐係話緊中國軍人唔係人係畜牲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T02:33:00.000Z","msg":"徽徽身在曹營心在漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7ebe0b009506080024499f1677424f501ed1f8","tid":2440389,"uid":359589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eed07c20973c35e9139fd9826a44e672d2c724e0","tid":2440389,"uid":359589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T02:31:34.000Z","msg":"造型好過鳩柏豪嗰個<im